---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";

const title = "Personal — Rachit Lohani";
const description = "Personal notes, interests, and reflections.";
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="page">
    <Nav />
    <main class="content">
      <header class="content-header">
        <p class="eyebrow">Personal</p>
        <h1>Warm notes from the path so far.</h1>
        <p class="lead">A little about my journey, what I care about, and the people who keep me grounded.</p>
      </header>

      <section class="content-block">
        <p>
          Rachit Lohani is a technology executive and builder with a long‑term focus on products
          that solve real problems. Across startups and large organizations, he’s known for
          connecting business intent to durable systems—while staying close to people and culture.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="content-block">
        <h2>Education and career</h2>
        <p>
          He studied in India and the U.S., with roots in Roorkee and graduate research at the
          University at Buffalo. Over the years, he has led teams and initiatives at companies
          including Intuit, Atlassian, AOL, E2open, and Paylocity—bringing a leadership style
          centered on clarity, creativity, and execution.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="content-block">
        <h2>Community and service</h2>
        <p>
          He’s passionate about increasing women’s participation in the workforce and expanding
          access to training and education for under‑represented talent in tech. These efforts
          shape how he mentors and invests time in the community.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="content-block">
        <h2>Home</h2>
        <p>
          Born in North India, Rachit moved to the U.S. for school and now lives in Northern
          California with his wife and two daughters. His proudest work is instilling in his
          daughters the values and love of learning his parents fostered in him.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="content-block">
        <h2>Moments</h2>
        <div class="photo-grid">
          <figure>
            <img src="https://rachitlohani.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/black-and-white.png" alt="Rachit Lohani portrait in black and white" loading="lazy" />
          </figure>
          <figure>
            <img src="https://rachitlohani.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/6c093-untitled-design-1.jpg" alt="Rachit Lohani speaking at an event" loading="lazy" />
          </figure>
          <figure>
            <img src="https://rachitlohani.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/b37c4-women-leadership-conference-sch-17.jpg" alt="Women in leadership conference moment" loading="lazy" />
          </figure>
          <figure>
            <img src="https://rachitlohani.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/f0180-img_0875.jpg" alt="Family moment" loading="lazy" />
          </figure>
          <figure>
            <img src="https://rachitlohani.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/904da-whatsapp-image-2024-06-13-at-08.10.30-1.jpeg" alt="Personal photo" loading="lazy" />
          </figure>
        </div>
      </section>

      <a class="button" href="/contact">Connect with me</a>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
